The Kebbi State Governor, Alhaji Abubakar Bagudu has assured National Youth Service Corps (NYSC) members of adequate security and better welfare in the state. The Governor, who was represented by his deputy, Alhaji Samaila Yombe gave the assurance at the swearing in ceremony of the NYSC batch C stream 1 members. According to him, various security agencies have been directed to double efforts towards giving maximum security to corps members and other citizens in the state. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .